{
  "stem": "11144.5",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And as I told you in the interview, I think I'm going to make a tape and send it to my nieces in Poland because I see that, especially the older one, is interested in the family whom she didn't know.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I mean, I didn't think that they were going to be proud of being Jewish, but they are not ashamed that they did come from a Jewish background.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, their mother was Jewish.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, my sister was Jewish.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, they were not raised as Jews.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's why I'm saying that I thought that they would be ashamed of being-- of coming from a Jewish background.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I asked the question when I was in Poland, and I know they are not.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They would like to have a tree really made up, which is a little hard for me because I don't remember everybody, and I, you know, don't know.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the older one was here in America and she really wanted to know how we survived, and how was the family, and how was this?",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And even my youngest niece's husband, who's Pole-- who's a Pole.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He's a very sweet nice guy.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They're both nice but he's really-- and he would like me to give him a tree so he can put in his daughter's book, so when the daughter grows up, knows the roots.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Which I thought, I was really very, very touched by it, because I didn't expect it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I mean, their mother didn't remember-- didn't remember her father because she was what, maybe five years old, or four years old when my father-- our father passed away.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She had no clue.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My stepfather was a father to her.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So she didn't know anything about it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I think that's why I decided.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
